des:
Now you (+/- friends) can put your USMLE STEP 1 knowledge to the test. This exam will quickly and efficiently identify any deficits in your understanding of USMLE immunology. It is our hope that with this skill, you will learn valuable, high-yield content in an enjoyable and unique manner. Cross-referenced with the most popular USMLE STEP 1 study materials, this quiz is ready to prepare you for your upcoming exam. Let's get started!
